            <title>[LU-7140] Few 4 MB BRW rpcs from readahead path</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7140</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have found that setting osc.max_pages_per_rpc=1024 leads to few 4 MB BRW rpcs.&lt;/p&gt;

